text: Kilinchi () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Kilinchinsky Selsoviet, Privolzhsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 3,137 as of 2010. There are 90 streets. == Geography == It is located 17 km from Astrakhan, 7 km from Nachalovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Privolzhsky District, Astrakhan Oblast
title: Kilinchi
